  "synopsis": "A cartoonist teenager who is running out of inspiration on his creative journey inadvertently adopts two pets when he goes out in search of inspiration. The cat is named Emperor and the dog is named Bazaar Black. Although the two little guys often caused him a lot of trouble, they also gained two pieces of companionship and love. Although they are a cat and a dog, the teenager knows that they are family. And so, the teenager's noisy but warm and happy life began.\n\n(Source: Bilibili)",
